comments.body: Feb 15. All applications submitted as of today have been checked and the results are added to the public spreadsheet. Please check your application status before proceeding to the tasks. Note that being accepted to the bounty does not mean you will assuredly earn reward stakes so make sure to complete the tasks honestly and completely. New applications submitted within the next 48 hours will be checked on Feb 17. Feb 18. Report forms for the first week are available. Please proceed to submit the tasks you completed from Feb 13 to 18. Report forms will be taken down on Sunday at midnight.Feb 20. Report forms for the first week are taken down. Please proceed to complete the tasks for Week 2 (Feb 20 to 25). Report forms for the second week will be available on Feb 25-26. Feb 25. Report forms for the second week are available. Please proceed to submit the tasks you completed from Feb 20 to 25. Report forms will be taken down on Sunday (Feb 26) at midnight.Feb 27. Report forms for the second week are taken down. Please proceed to complete the tasks for Week 3 (Feb 27 to March 4). Report forms for the third week will be available on March 4-5. March 4. Report forms for the third week are available. Please proceed to submit the tasks you completed from Feb 27 to March 4. Report forms will be taken down on Sunday (March 5) at midnight.March 6. Report forms for the third week are taken down. Please proceed to complete the tasks for Week 4 (March 6 to 11). Report forms for the fourth week will be available on March 11-12. March 11. Report forms for the fourth week are available. Please proceed to submit the tasks you completed from March 6 to March 11. Report forms will be taken down on Sunday (March 12) at midnight.March 13. Report forms for the fourth week are taken down. This round of the Zenland Bounty Campaign is now over. Stakes earned by participants of this round will be checked within the next 4 weeks and the rewards will be distributed on April 12. Zenland team thanks everyone who took honest participation and contributed to spreading our word!This post is reserved for important announcements related to the bounty campaign.
